Class RegisterSubscriberFrameController

java.lang.Object
gui.RegisterSubscriberFrameController
All Implemented Interfaces:
IController
public class RegisterSubscriberFrameController extends Object implements IController
Controller class for the Register Subscriber Frame UI. Handles subscriber registration form input, validation, and submission.
